Z","msg":"收唔到條尾數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T01:41:56.000Z","msg":"支那人本性，拖十世都唔找數甚至走數，所以專家反轉豬肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7339943a4a3515523029da03fd8a9349773fa53","tid":2413651,"uid":375135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2ff45b6efac657c6ce984090921ba431db3971a","tid":2413651,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T00:57:36.000Z","msg":"世界衛生組織（WHO）專家目前已經將病毒源頭範圍縮小，將焦點放在武漢華南海鮮市場販賣的鼬獾與兔子身上。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n世衛專家小組成員達薩克（Peter Daszak）表示，華南海鮮市場冷凍庫發現的動物屍體中有鼬獾，儘管檢測病毒呈陰性反應，但鼬獾仍然有可能是病毒宿主。鼬獾與鼬鼠、水獺同屬鼬科，在中國主要分布在華南地區，雖然是保育類動物，但常被獵捕作為食物或毛皮交易。<br />\n<br />\n達薩克也說，華南海鮮市場也有發現兔子的蹤跡，而兔類很容易感染由武漢肺炎引起的SARS-CoV-2病毒。世衛團隊中的荷蘭病毒學家古柏曼斯（Marion Koopmans）也將華南海鮮市場中的鼬獾與兔子列為疑似帶有並傳播武漢肺炎的動物。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3442974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3442974&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69MLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=2bc27a8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3442974&h=bd2b0ae2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3442974</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T01:42:21.000Z","msg":"浸馮同負珍重唔出黎護主"},{"pid":"819dc67de43d69fb37f0bef09fe5836f2d279d90","tid":2413651,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3c4f1f775e9a2319356291720f8468f5e2e2dab","tid":2413651,"uid":154429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T01:37:54.000Z","msg":"今日先有咩，戇撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"